Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.73,0:00:04.10,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Yeah, it's done.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.10,0:00:07.67,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I'll send it this week, so make sure you watch for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.67,0:00:10.61,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I'm glad I finally wrote an outstanding calligraphy piece.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.61,0:00:14.18,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Ever since I've been here,\NI've been tingling with inspiration.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.77,0:00:16.01,Dialogue2,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\an5\pos(360,45)}"Narukain Exhibit Application
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.77,0:00:16.01,Dialogue2,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\an5\pos(360,73)}'Stars'"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.18,0:00:16.38,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Got to hand it to Mother Nature.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.38,0:00:21.45,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I'm actually enjoying writing, compared to when I was over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.45,0:00:24.25,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Hey, are you listening, Kawafuji?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.25,0:00:26.35,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.35,0:00:30.96,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,You're early, Director. I'm sorry to have put you to the trouble of coming here.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.96,0:00:33.86,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,How is his work going?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.86,0:00:36.53,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,He says he's doing fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.53,0:00:39.53,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Instead of writing beautiful calligraphy like others...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.53,0:00:43.64,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,...I'd prefer that Handa-{\i1}k u n{\i0} master writing calligraphy of his own.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.64,0:00:47.44,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,A calligraphy that represents his very self...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.44,0:00:49.08,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I don't know about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.08,0:00:53.11,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Personally, I'd rather like him to hurry on back here,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.11,0:00:56.41,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,but he seems intent not to return until he gets results from the exhibit.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.09,0:01:02.26,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Has he... repented for punching me?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.26,0:01:04.56,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Well, I can't answer that...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.56,0:01:08.63,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,If my forgiveness will bring him back...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.63,0:01:11.73,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,...let's have him come back soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.53,0:02:47.00,Dialogue2,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\an5\pos(361,42)}"Dacchi Ikode"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.53,0:02:47.00,Dialogue2,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\an5\pos(361,76)}"Translation: Let's go together"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.50,0:02:52.66,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Damn that Kawafuji...\NHe doesn't care what I have to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.57,0:02:57.54,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I expressed myself strongly to Kawafuji, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.67,0:02:59.84,Dialogue2,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\an5\pos(360,45)}"Narukain Exhibit Application
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.67,0:02:59.84,Dialogue2,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\an5\pos(360,73)}'Stars'"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.54,0:03:00.61,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,...was that calligraphy really okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.84,0:03:05.41,Dialogue2,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\an5\pos(360,42)}"Stars"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.61,0:03:01.88,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I think it looks good...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.88,0:03:05.78,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,You can tell it was written in the heat of the moment...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.78,0:03:09.12,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Can I really say this is my calligraphy?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.12,0:03:11.69,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,This is something I was able to write because I was on the island.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.69,0:03:15.96,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,If I was told to write the same in Tokyo, I probably couldn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.96,0:03:18.76,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Dang it... Now I'm getting worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.76,0:03:23.87,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Is it okay to submit something I wrote on a whim to an exhibit I can't afford to lose?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.87,0:03:25.37,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Positive... Positive thinking...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.37,0:03:27.47,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,It's no use thinking about it now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.47,0:03:30.87,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,My only weapon now is my inspiration from nature.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.87,0:03:34.74,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Worrying about my calligraphy would push the schedule...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.74,0:03:36.78,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Naru, what do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.78,0:03:37.95,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Huh? What?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.95,0:03:40.62,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Never mind that. Whatcha wanna play today?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.62,0:03:41.72,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Never mind...?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.72,0:03:43.48,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I'm not going to play with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.48,0:03:46.45,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Here I was trying to open up to you in a rare moment of vulnerability...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.45,0:03:49.56,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Better watch what ya say...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.56,0:03:51.06,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,--Peek...\N--Tch!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.96,0:03:53.13,Dialogue2,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\an5\pos(360,45)}"'I'll do anything you say' ticket
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.96,0:03:53.13,Dialogue2,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\an5\pos(361,73)}1 time"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.06,0:03:53.49,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I should have made a "free shoulder massage" ticket instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.49,0:03:56.63,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,As long as I got this, ya gotta listen to what I say forever!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.63,0:03:59.57,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,It says "1 time" on there, got it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.57,0:04:00.60,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.60,0:04:02.57,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Grandpa!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.57,0:04:03.84,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.84,0:04:05.11,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Naru!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.11,0:04:06.24,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.24,0:04:07.97,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,What are they doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.44,0:04:14.48,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Ya stack them stones ta make a wall to protect against hurricanes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.48,0:04:17.69,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Ya gotta stack 'em perfect, or else it'll just fall apart.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.69,0:04:19.32,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,It's like a puzzle.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.32,0:04:22.32,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Then can ya bring me that stone over there?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.32,0:04:25.16,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,He's trying to make it so\NI just naturally start helping!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.16,0:04:28.96,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Naru's gonna make Sensei take her toad huntin'... using this!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.96,0:04:30.16,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Toad hunting?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.16,0:04:31.60,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,--'Kay, then...\N--Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.60,0:04:33.94,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I'll use this, so help me out, will ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.94,0:04:35.54,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,--Wha--?!\N--Well, if that's the case...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.54,0:04:38.01,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Aww! That's Naru's!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.01,0:04:40.51,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,C'mon, I'll give ya somethin' else, Naru.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.51,0:04:43.21,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Somethin' else? Whatcha mean by that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.21,0:04:45.15,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,--Here.\N--Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.78,0:04:47.88,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.88,0:04:51.05,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,It's a rock that'll skip good on water.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.05,0:04:53.12,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Aah... Aren't you happy, Naru?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.12,0:04:56.46,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Don't want it...!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.46,0:04:57.66,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Pretty good.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.66,0:04:59.65,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,C'mon and help, Sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.33,0:05:04.50,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,S-So heavy...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.50,0:05:06.20,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Take it there.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.20,0:05:07.40,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Phooey...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.40,0:05:10.07,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Let's put this...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.07,0:05:11.56,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,...here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.84,0:05:14.98,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,It feels good when it fits in perfectly!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.98,0:05:17.31,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Ya don't say?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.19,0:05:27.59,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Yer really good.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.59,0:05:30.26,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I think I'm good at handling exacting tasks.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.26,0:05:34.73,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I thought I stacked mine well, but this here's rickety.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.73,0:05:37.70,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Pfft...! You've got no skills, Grandpa!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.17,0:05:41.19,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,You're so honest, Naru!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.57,0:05:46.94,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Why not have Sensei handle that shrine thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.94,0:05:49.04,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah, that thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.04,0:05:50.53,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,That thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.05,0:05:57.12,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Go on in.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.12,0:05:58.61,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.59,0:06:04.06,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,What is it that I have to do in this shrine? Purification?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.06,0:06:06.19,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Look at that there.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.19,0:06:09.26,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Them's the names of the people who helped when the shrine was built.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.26,0:06:11.70,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Well, it's got all of us villagers' names there.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.70,0:06:14.60,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,We're thinkin' of getting it rewritten.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.60,0:06:16.77,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Here ya go.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.77,0:06:18.21,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,A list of names.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.21,0:06:22.31,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,We were gonna hire a pro from the city to rewrite it, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.31,0:06:24.98,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,...you're better, right, Sensei?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.98,0:06:26.47,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.25,0:06:32.15,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Wow... This is amazing. So old...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.15,0:06:35.29,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,It ain't much, but we'll pay, y'know?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.29,0:06:37.43,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Ah, I'm not worried about the pay, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.43,0:06:38.83,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Don't feel like it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.83,0:06:41.23,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,That's not it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.23,0:06:45.93,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,It's just that it's been a while since\NI wrote such well-ordered characters.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.93,0:06:49.27,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Write 'em good, 'kay?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.27,0:06:52.14,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Ya see here? Got space here for one more person.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.14,0:06:56.14,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Sensei, can ya write yer name down here, so we know who did the writin'?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.14,0:06:58.61,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Are you sure? I didn't contribute at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.61,0:06:59.61,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Shh...!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.61,0:07:00.85,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Keep it secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.85,0:07:02.75,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Uh, that's not good...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.82,0:07:09.46,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,--Sensei.\N--Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.46,0:07:12.63,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,There was a call from\NKawafuji-{\i1}s a n{\i0} for you at the store.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.63,0:07:15.60,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,That guy... And after ignoring me too...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.63,0:07:18.70,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,You kids go and take this back to my place.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.70,0:07:20.19,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.87,0:07:27.21,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Why'd Kawafuji call?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.21,0:07:29.31,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,He said he had something important to talk about.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.31,0:07:30.98,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Whatcha mean, important to talk 'bout?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.98,0:07:32.84,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Adult talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.12,0:07:35.65,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,What's the matter, Naru?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.65,0:07:40.89,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I didn't get to ask for anything with my "I'll do anything you say" ticket...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.89,0:07:43.19,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Grandpa used it up!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.19,0:07:45.33,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,That's too bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.33,0:07:48.06,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,What were you going to ask for, Naru?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.06,0:07:49.73,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Lemme see...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.73,0:07:52.53,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I wanna go to the festival with Sensei, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.53,0:07:54.90,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,...I wanna go to the sea again too!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.90,0:07:57.17,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I wanna go to a sports event too!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.17,0:07:58.51,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Hey, the mountains, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.51,0:07:59.81,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.81,0:08:03.74,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I bet he'd take you to those places without a ticket.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.74,0:08:04.88,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.88,0:08:06.65,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I can't wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.65,0:08:09.35,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,C'mon, let's plan for goin' to the festival!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.35,0:08:11.02,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Hina wants to wear a kimono!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.02,0:08:13.19,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Then let's ask Miwa-{\i1}n e e{\i0} and Tama to come too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.19,0:08:15.39,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,It'll become a hassle if you invite those two.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.39,0:08:16.86,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,You're gonna come too, right, Akki?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.86,0:08:18.35,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Yup.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.36,0:08:25.37,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Yeah... I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.37,0:08:27.87,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Yeah, I got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.87,0:08:29.36,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I'll return.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.07,0:08:34.71,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Okay! I'll choose this one!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.71,0:08:36.11,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I'll use this.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.11,0:08:39.75,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Good! You've both done well, improving yourselves through all the lessons.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.75,0:08:42.68,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,As your mentor, there's nothing more I can teach you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.68,0:08:45.29,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,You both better get a gold award!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.02,0:08:46.29,Dialogue2,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\an5\pos(360,45)}"Visiting Old, Learning New"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.29,0:08:46.88,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.03,0:08:53.23,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,That's 'bout it for bein' eager.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.23,0:08:55.10,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Is this really gonna be okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.10,0:08:58.87,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,With all that spirit we put into it, if we don't get awarded...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.87,0:09:00.57,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I feel sick about submitting this...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.57,0:09:02.10,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,You idiots!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.10,0:09:03.54,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I taught you two!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.54,0:09:06.07,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Your calligraphy won't lose to anyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.07,0:09:09.28,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Ya really think so, Sensei?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.28,0:09:11.31,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I'm the one who should be worried...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.31,0:09:16.15,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I'm not even sure if the work I'm going to submit is good or not...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.15,0:09:18.09,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.09,0:09:20.45,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Sensei! Take us to the festival!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.45,0:09:22.29,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,You promised!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.29,0:09:28.26,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Here you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.26,0:09:30.33,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Sensei, I didn't know you could tie a yukata sash.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.33,0:09:32.30,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,That's amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.30,0:09:33.73,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,It's cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.73,0:09:35.57,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,This is nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.57,0:09:39.14,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,If I wanted to, I could tie a kimono sash too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.14,0:09:40.84,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Sensei, you're going to the festival too, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.84,0:09:41.91,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.91,0:09:44.01,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Yaaay! Let's hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.01,0:09:45.48,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Festival! Festival!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.48,0:09:48.28,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,'Kay, we're gonna go too, so see you there.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.28,0:09:49.95,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,--Thanks for the calligraphy.\N--Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.95,0:09:51.95,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Sensei, let's hurry and go!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.95,0:09:54.65,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,--Hurry...!\N--I got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.36,0:09:57.76,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,A festival...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.76,0:09:59.69,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I guess I'll go with them for a change of pace.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.69,0:10:01.43,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Sensei, you look happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.43,0:10:04.27,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I-I'm not happy at all, you know!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.27,0:10:05.50,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.50,0:10:07.66,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Festival!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.00,0:10:12.31,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Oh, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.31,0:10:13.93,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,This'll be the last...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.88,0:10:21.98,Dialogue2,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\an5\pos(360,42)}"Goto Bus Center"
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.85,0:10:22.61,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Yay! Festival! Festival!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.65,0:10:27.55,Dialogue2,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\an5\pos(361,42)}"Tonme Festival"
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.39,0:10:31.66,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Sensei! Here! Over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.33,0:10:35.63,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,So this is what a festival is like...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.63,0:10:39.63,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Come to think of it, I hardly went to any when I was in Tokyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.23,0:10:43.80,Dialogue2,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\an5\pos(361,45)}"Elementary School"
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.63,0:10:41.90,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Sei-{\i1}s a n{\i0}? How would you like to go to the festival?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.90,0:10:44.57,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,No. He has an exhibit to attend to.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.04,0:10:49.54,Dialogue2,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\an5\pos(361,45)}"High School"
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.57,0:10:46.84,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Handa, let's go to the festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.84,0:10:50.38,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I'm sorry. Sei-{\i1}s a n{\i0} has an exhibit to attend to.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.81,0:10:55.65,Dialogue2,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\an5\pos(360,45)}"College"
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.38,0:10:52.41,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Handa-{\i1}k y u n{\i0}, let's go to the festival!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.41,0:10:55.05,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Handa's got an exhibit he has to attend to, so I'll go in his place.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.05,0:10:56.35,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.35,0:11:00.09,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Sad memories to remember... and even now, it's before an exhibit.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.09,0:11:01.82,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.26,0:11:03.72,Dialogue2,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\an5\pos(361,45)}"Goldfish Scoop"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.82,0:11:04.16,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Sensei! Goldfish! Goldfish!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.16,0:11:06.99,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Oh! That's the famous goldfish scoop!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.10,0:11:12.17,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Oh! Yer here too, Sensei?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.17,0:11:15.54,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Yakuza--! No, you're Miwa's dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.54,0:11:17.61,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I'm just helpin' out the association.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.61,0:11:19.37,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Wow, you must be busy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.37,0:11:21.21,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Here ya go... 100 yen.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.58,0:11:24.78,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,A pastry shell?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.78,0:11:26.61,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,You can scoop with this?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.61,0:11:28.22,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Do yer best, Sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.22,0:11:29.71,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Your best!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.02,0:11:37.51,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Now!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.63,0:11:41.96,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,--Huh?\N--You're bad at this, Sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.96,0:11:43.90,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Pops, this has got to be defective!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.90,0:11:45.90,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Course it ain't. Yer just bad at it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.90,0:11:48.04,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Damn it... Once more...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.04,0:11:50.44,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Excuse me, Sensei. Can you move over a bit?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.44,0:11:51.61,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Ah, Nurse?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.61,0:11:52.97,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Hey! Iku-{\i1}n e e{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.97,0:11:55.41,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,You're not supposed to scoop with force.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.41,0:11:58.21,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Keep yer eyes on Iku-{\i1}chan{\i0}'s scoopin' skills.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.49,0:12:08.56,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Wh-What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.56,0:12:11.62,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,It's as if the goldfish are coming in to be scooped!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.66,0:12:14.60,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Hey... It's Iku!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.60,0:12:18.47,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Amazin' as usual. She's gonna put us in the red.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.47,0:12:21.17,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I'd like ta know what she's gonna do with all of 'em.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.17,0:12:22.17,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,True...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.17,0:12:24.43,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,--Here's the last spurt...\N--Iku!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.94,0:12:27.74,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Whatcha doing, Aiko?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.74,0:12:30.24,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Too bad, Iku-{\i1}c h a n.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.24,0:12:32.94,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Aww... And I was so close to making a new record!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.01,0:12:37.08,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Ikuko tries to make a clean sweep at the goldfish scoop every year.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.08,0:12:39.42,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Huh? Head Teacher?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.42,0:12:43.49,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Thought I taught her the importance of moderation back in branch school...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.49,0:12:46.59,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Huh, is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.59,0:12:50.19,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,He wants me to call him out, but I'm not taking the bait.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.50,0:12:54.44,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,We didn't catch any goldfish.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.44,0:12:58.00,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Raising living things is a pain, so I purposely didn't catch any.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.34,0:13:01.38,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,They're doin' somethin' over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.38,0:13:02.61,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Wonder what.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.61,0:13:03.94,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,It's a free throw competition.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.94,0:13:05.88,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,--Hey, Akki!\N--A-Akki?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.88,0:13:09.72,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,You shoot for points as a four-person team for coupons.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.72,0:13:11.22,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,We're gonna enter too!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.22,0:13:12.29,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,You brats!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.29,0:13:13.65,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,We're on the same team.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.65,0:13:16.99,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,If it weren't for the middle school students so serious about the coupons,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.99,0:13:19.36,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,we would have had a solid chance for first place.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.36,0:13:21.16,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,First place is 5,000 yen...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.16,0:13:23.96,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Let's show everyone that the softball club is invincible.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.96,0:13:25.57,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Okay, Miwa-{\i1}c c h i.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.57,0:13:27.23,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,The air there is stagnant...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.23,0:13:29.34,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Hey, isn't Tama with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.34,0:13:30.87,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Oh, Sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.87,0:13:33.64,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Tama went to buy today's manga release.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.64,0:13:37.88,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,We gotta have four people, so I want her to come back soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.88,0:13:39.55,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,It's the rumored Sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.55,0:13:42.04,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Wow, he's handsome!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.86,0:13:51.36,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Nice, Akki!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.36,0:13:54.36,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Akki's actin' sassy for a sixth grader.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.36,0:13:58.00,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Contrary to his appearance,\NAkki is pretty high-spec.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.00,0:14:01.04,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,It's our turn next, but where in the world is Tama?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.04,0:14:02.54,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,So late!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.04,0:14:07.44,Dialogue2,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\an5\pos(361,42)}"Tama at the time"
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.54,0:14:06.17,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Why don't you have it on sale on the day of release?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.17,0:14:08.08,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,It's always been like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.08,0:14:10.51,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Next up, "Softball Club Eyeglasses Team"!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.51,0:14:12.58,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,This isn't good, Miwa-{\i1}c c h i...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.58,0:14:15.02,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Hurry and come down!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.02,0:14:17.68,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Why, that rotten four-eyes...!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.05,0:14:20.25,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Sensei! Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.25,0:14:22.62,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,--Huh?!\N--You just have ta make a shot in!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.62,0:14:24.86,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,--Just make a shot in?! It isn't that easy!\N--Okay, first shot!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.86,0:14:27.13,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Alley-oop!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.13,0:14:28.72,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Second shot!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.03,0:14:32.73,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Third shot!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.44,0:14:37.20,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,You girls are too good!\NAren't you in the softball club?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.20,0:14:39.91,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,We sometimes help the basketball club too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.91,0:14:43.04,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,None of the clubs have many members, so we give an' take, y'know?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.04,0:14:44.88,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,The club situation in the countryside is astounding...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.88,0:14:47.05,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Here! Now do it, Sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.05,0:14:48.78,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Huh? Seriously?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.78,0:14:50.78,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I guess I don't have a choice...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.78,0:14:52.82,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Sensei! Do yer best!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.82,0:14:56.96,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Who'd have expected a day to arrive where I would have to display my undisclosed talent...?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.96,0:14:59.13,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,That's right... I used to...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.13,0:15:01.25,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,...read basketball manga!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.50,0:15:09.64,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,The winner, "Team Akki"! They did great, even as elementary students! So moving!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.64,0:15:12.61,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Sensei? Lift yer spirits...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.61,0:15:15.94,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Well... I thought I could do it...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.94,0:15:17.61,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Here, Sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.61,0:15:20.58,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,It ain't much, but we got some coupons for second place.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.58,0:15:22.85,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Even split fer 300 yen a head.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.85,0:15:25.15,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,You sure I can have these, even when I missed?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.15,0:15:28.82,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Should've been Tama's, but she ain't comin'.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.32,0:15:35.30,Dialogue2,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\an5\pos(361,42)}"Tama at the time"
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.82,0:15:32.29,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I asked you to put the book on hold!\NWhy'd you sell it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.29,0:15:33.79,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,We'll get more soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.79,0:15:36.00,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,To heck with it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.30,0:15:39.47,Dialogue2,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\an5\pos(361,45)}"Takoyaki 400
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.30,0:15:39.47,Dialogue2,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\an5\pos(360,73)}Yakisoba 300
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.30,0:15:39.47,Dialogue2,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\an5\pos(361,107)}Cotton Candy 100
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.30,0:15:39.47,Dialogue2,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\an5\pos(360,135)}Juice 150"
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.00,0:15:38.97,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,What do you want to eat?\NI'll buy you anything now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.97,0:15:40.13,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.13,0:15:41.27,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Then, {\i1}t a k o y a k i{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.27,0:15:42.47,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ya k i s o b a{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.47,0:15:44.14,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,--Cotton candy it is.\N--Huh...?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.14,0:15:47.14,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,--Cheap!\N--Ya said anything we want!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.14,0:15:49.81,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Don't think that all adults have money with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.81,0:15:52.31,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,It's okay, then. I'll just buy it myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.31,0:15:53.38,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Hina too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.38,0:15:56.78,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,You girls had money?!\NI showed off for nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.78,0:16:00.15,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,If ya want something, lemme know.\NI'll buy it for ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.15,0:16:04.16,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Stop it! No way I can be treated by a seven-year-old kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.16,0:16:05.82,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Just let her treat you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.99,0:16:08.16,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Hiro!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.16,0:16:13.30,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Wanna buy some {\i1}y a k i s o b a{\i0}?\NIt'll help fund the baseball club.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.30,0:16:16.07,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Not that I don't have money, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.07,0:16:18.47,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I'll have three cotton candies, using these coupons.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.47,0:16:20.63,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,So cheap...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.31,0:16:24.71,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Here, super-sized.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.71,0:16:25.91,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.91,0:16:27.85,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,--Here.\N--Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.85,0:16:30.15,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,--Here, Sensei.\N--Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.15,0:16:32.42,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Thanks, Sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.42,0:16:35.49,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,So this is cotton candy...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.49,0:16:37.09,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Where am I supposed to bite into it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.09,0:16:39.36,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Here? Over here?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.36,0:16:42.50,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Wait, here? No, here?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.50,0:16:45.73,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Is Sensei going to be all right walking into the crowd?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.73,0:16:47.60,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Hope he doesn't get cotton candy on someone's clothes,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.60,0:16:49.44,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,or poke himself with the chopstick...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.44,0:16:51.87,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Hiroshi! We got more {\i1}y a k i s o b a{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.55,0:17:00.18,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Them drums are so loud!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.18,0:17:01.74,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,So loud!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.31,0:17:30.64,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,The fireworks display will begin at nine o'clock.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.64,0:17:32.31,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Fireworks, Sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.31,0:17:34.25,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.25,0:17:37.58,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Both of you, don't get lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.58,0:17:38.65,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.65,0:17:41.09,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Sensei! Over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.09,0:17:43.11,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Already...?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.66,0:17:46.43,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Naru!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.43,0:17:48.23,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Hina!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.23,0:17:50.16,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Damn it! It's so dark...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.16,0:17:51.63,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Sensei...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.63,0:17:53.83,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Tama? What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.83,0:17:55.97,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I was reading the manga I bought.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.97,0:17:57.67,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I don't like being in a crowd.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.67,0:18:01.24,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I'm pretty much like this every year during the summer festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.24,0:18:04.91,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Not that I'm fit to say this, but you're wasting your youth badly.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.91,0:18:08.12,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Did you see Naru and Hina--stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.12,0:18:11.11,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,They went through here, so they must have gone to the beach.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.75,0:18:15.12,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,It's almost time for the fireworks, so let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.12,0:18:16.99,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,We know a perfect place.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.16,0:18:24.43,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Hey, it's Sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.43,0:18:26.47,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Tama, where ya been hiding?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.47,0:18:28.94,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I'm really sorry. I was just reading manga.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.94,0:18:30.70,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Huh? Where are the girls from the softball club?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.70,0:18:33.37,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,They're gonna watch the fireworks with their boyfriends.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.37,0:18:35.28,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Oh? If only they'd explode...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.28,0:18:38.38,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,--Tama?!\N--Hey! Naru and Hina're here too!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.38,0:18:39.48,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.48,0:18:41.65,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,You're here too, Hiro-{\i1}n i i{\i0}?\NWhere's yer girlfriend?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.65,0:18:44.02,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,You think I'd be cooking {\i1}y a k i s o b a{\i0} if I had a girlfriend?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.02,0:18:46.05,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Sorry, I was just pullin' yer leg.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.05,0:18:48.29,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Well, I guess it's the same group as usual.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.29,0:18:49.78,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Yup.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.03,0:18:54.06,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,So, summer vacation is about to end...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.06,0:18:56.16,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,It was fun this year.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.16,0:18:59.37,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Once school starts, we won't be able to play so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.37,0:19:01.34,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Hiro-{\i1}n i i{\i0}, you gonna study for the exam?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.07,0:19:04.91,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I'm gonna look for a job.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.91,0:19:07.67,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Does that mean you're gonna stay on the island?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.67,0:19:10.04,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,--I'm leaving.\N--Aww... That's going to be sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.04,0:19:12.21,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Well, I still got some time.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.21,0:19:15.85,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,I guess, and even if Hiro-{\i1}n i i{\i0} ain't 'round, we still got Sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.85,0:19:18.48,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,You think Sensei can take my place?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.52,0:19:21.92,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.92,0:19:24.19,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,There's something I need to say...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.33,0:19:34.39,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,It's starting!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.04,0:19:39.57,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Yikes! It's so bright!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.57,0:19:41.91,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,--Wow!\N--Super!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.88,0:19:48.12,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.12,0:19:50.35,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,What was Sensei trying to say?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.35,0:19:53.25,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,--Beats me...\N--Both of ya, look at him.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.92,0:19:58.79,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Even without words, Sensei's back says it all...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.24,0:20:48.44,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Sensei! I'm here to play!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.01,0:20:51.50,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.99,0:21:01.42,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.42,0:21:02.91,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.86,0:21:07.59,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,Sensei...?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.09,0:22:49.22,Dialogue1,Unknown,0,0,0,,No one's a comin'...
